text.section:
The report shall provide the following information for each county:
the type of 9-1-1 system currently operating in the county;
the total 9-1-1 fee and additional charge charged;
the funding formula in effect;
any statutory or regulatory violation by the county and the response of the Board;
any efforts to establish an enhanced 9-1-1 system in the county; and
any suggested changes to this subtitle.
